#  Advanced Level Task

##  Cricket Fielding Analysis

###  Description

This project analyzes IPL fielding data to evaluate player performance using a **Performance Score (PS)**.

The program cleans real-world messy data and identifies the best fielder.

---

##  Features

* Reads CSV/Excel data using pandas
* Cleans and formats data
* Converts Y/N values to numeric format
* Calculates Performance Score
* Identifies best fielder

---

##  Performance Score Formula

```
PS = Pick + Throw + Runs Saved
```

(Can be extended to include catches, run-outs, etc.)

---

##  Files

* `Advanced_level_Task_Shadow_Fox.py`
* `IPL_SAMPLE_DATA.csv`


## How to Run

### 1️ Install Requirements

```bash
pip install pandas
```

### 2️ Run the program

```bash
python Advanced_level_Task_Shadow_Fox.py


---

##  Sample Output

```
Player Performance:
Rilee Rossouw   10
Yash Dhull      11

Best Fielder: Yash Dhull
Score: 11
```

